ets identified. The implementation uses local state and deterministic hashing for request building.\n\n## Quality\nCode is clean, idiomatic, and well-tested. The integration into `duet_composer.py` correctly threads the module-level state into the `learning` dictionary to fix the throttle regression.\n\n## Issues Found\nNone.\n\n## Verdict: PASS\n\n## Notes for Lead Agent\nThe implementation is solid and addresses the regression noted in T-013. The tests are comprehensive.\n","file_path":"sdp/verification/t-014 @20260427t001208z-verify.md"}}
