m.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n- Follow existing code style and patterns.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n- Do not clean, revert, commit, or otherwise normalize unrelated pre-existing\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n  workspace changes.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n- Commit your working change immediately.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n## Validation\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nRun this command before finishing:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n```bash\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\npytest tests/ -x --tb=short && ruff check src/ tests/ && mypy src/\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n```\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"}\\\\\\\\n./sdp/logs/Lead_T-021_20260416T181925Z_1776393558.log:48:{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"type\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"tool_use\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"timestamp\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"2026-04-17T02:40:12.200Z\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"tool_name\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"run_shell_command\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"tool_id\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"run_shell_command_1776393612200_0\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"parameters\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\":{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"command\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"pytest tests/test_motif_memory.py\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"}}\\\\\\\\n./sdp/logs/Lead_T-021_20260416T181925Z_1776393558.log:50:{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"type\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"tool_result\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"timestamp\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"2026-04-17T02:40:13.756Z\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"tool_id\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"run_shell_command_1776393612200_0\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"status\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"success\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"output\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"/opt/anaconda3/lib/python3.11/site-packages/pytest_asyncio/plugin.py:252: PytestDeprecationWarning: The configuration option \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"asyncio_default_fixture_loop_scope\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\" is unset.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nThe event loop scope for asynchronous fixtures will default to the fixture caching scope. Future versions of pytest-asyncio will default the loo